Package: darkcrawler
Version: 2.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: tor, python, libxml2, libxslt, clang, python-lxml, git
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/Anon4You/DarkCrawler
Description: CLI tool to crawl .onion sites and generate threat reports
 DarkCrawler crawls .onion sites through the Tor network, performs
 real‑time content threat analysis, and produces structured threat
 intelligence reports.
